channel.title: Happy birthday to me, martin, starblaster, pancake man, kurt kobain
channel.description:
Sup Gee's. I'm 15 this very day! Probably getting money, this is the birthday where all the magic has gone lol. not having a party either, did most of my partying on sunday with the missus ;). going to school in a bit probably gonna get birthday beats(sp) bad.
what im most probably getting: money so i can buy a new guitar.
rate/hate/masturbate
edit - i forgot to say happy pancake day...
edit - according to mopar you americans dont eat pancakes on pancake day, its not a big thing just ... eat pancakes!
